  "original_title": "\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0bae\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0b95\u0b9a\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1 3 \u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba9\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "3 fishermen who went fishing in Thalaimannar sea are missing",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "It has been reported that three fishermen who went to the sea in a boat from Thalaimannar Pier are missing, but the said three fishermen are being searched for and there is no information about them from anywhere.",
        "Three fishermen belonging to Thalaimannar Pier, Rasathurai Rasasekar (52 years old), Rajamurthy Mohanraj (50 years old) and Raji Janath (27 years old) as usual, from Thalaimannar Pier sector to catch net fish in the North Sea on Thursday 14th in an outboard motor boat (boat) .OVRB-A-4138 MNRI) have departed.",
        "Since they did not return to the shore as usual, the fishermen and marines of this area are searching from Friday 15th until today.",
        "But till the 16th Saturday, it is reported that neither they nor the boat they went to have been found. It is also reported that strong winds have been blowing in this area for the past couple of days."
      ],
